Marvin GEORGE, Appellant, v. The STATE of Florida, Appellee. No. 75-1304. District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. May 11, 1976.

May 11, 1976.

Philip A. Hubbart, Public Defender, and Elliot H. Scherker, Asst. Public Defender, for appellant. Robert L. Shevin, Atty. Gen., and Ira N. Loewy, Asst. Atty. Gen., for appellee. Before HAVERFIELD and NATHAN, JJ., and CHARLES CARROLL, (Ret.), Associate Judge. PER CURIAM.

Affirmed. See State v. Kelley, Fla.App.1975, 322 So.2d 581; Eastwood v. Hall, Fla.App.1972, 258 So.2d 269.
